<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrījayalakṣmīnātha<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> svabhujābalavijitaparadharādhipa
<lb n="2" break="no"/>yūthassa jayati vibhavamahēṁdrō jagati kulōttuṁggacōḍa
<lb n="3" break="no"/>goṁkanarēṁdraḥ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 1*] yasya pratāpaprabalānalārccirddagdhā<unclear>nya</unclear>bhūbhṛ
<lb n="4" break="no"/>dvaradhāmarājirbhītānyarakṣāmaniśaṁ praku<unclear>rvva</unclear>nkōpaprasā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>dadvayamadvi<unclear>bhā</unclear>ti [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 2*] tadgoṁkakṣiti<unclear>pa</unclear>kramabhaktērācaraṇavidyayā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>cāryyatayā <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> yuktaḥ kūtayanāmna ścelvāṁbāyāssupu
<lb n="7" break="no"/>trakaḥ pātranidhiḥ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 3*] śrīviśvakarmmamunivaravaṁśakaraḥ kāntiviji
<lb n="8" break="no"/>tasitarugnā<unclear>nā</unclear>bharaṇācāryyō<supplied reason="omitted">yō</supplied> jayati sa bhuvi karmmarābharaṇaḥ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 4*] sauja
<lb n="9" break="no"/>nyapuṇyanilayō nūṁkāṁḍissuprasiddhapaurṣanirata<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> svaguṇamaṇigaṇa
<lb n="10" break="no"/>vibhūṣaṇabhūṣitamitrō virājatē sucaritraḥ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 5*] kararasaviyadiṁ<unclear>du</unclear>mi
<lb n="11" break="no"/>tē śakarājasamōtkarē śubhayuktē <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> kārttikasitapaṁcamyāṁ gurusi
<lb n="12" break="no"/><unclear>ddha</unclear>dinē suyōga<unclear>yu</unclear>tē [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 6*] nādiṁ<unclear>ḍla</unclear>mūla<supplied reason="omitted">saṁ</supplied>sthitacaṁdradharāya pradīpamā
<lb n="13" break="no"/>caṁdrārkkaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> prādātsa vaṁśadīpō nūṁkāṁḍi<unclear>r</unclear>ggoṁkamaṁḍalikapadabhaktaḥ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 7*]
<lb n="14"/>śrīmanmahāmaṁḍalēśvara kulōttuṁgacōḍagoṁkkarājuna kiṣṭabhrityuṁḍu
<lb n="15" break="no"/>nu viśvakarmmakulasaṁbhavuṁḍunu jananāthanaṁdanuṁḍunaina kūtāṁ<unclear>ḍi</unclear>
<lb n="16"/><unclear>koḍu</unclear>ku nūṁkāṁḍi śakavarṣamulu 1063 gunēṇṭi viṣuvuna nādiṁḍla
<lb n="17"/>śrīmūlasthānamahādēvara kakhaṁḍava<unclear>r</unclear>ttidīpaṁbuna kiccina goṟiya
<lb n="18" break="no"/><unclear>lu</unclear> 55 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> vīniṁ jēkoni yācakamārebōyukoḍuku gaṁḍe putrā<unclear>nu</unclear>
<lb n="19" break="no"/>pautrakamu nitya māneṁḍu neyi dīpamunakuṁ bōyaṁgalavā<unclear>ṁḍu</unclear> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
<lb n="20"/>¿ svadattāṁ paradattāṁ vā yō harēta vasuṁ<unclear>da</unclear>rā<unclear>ṁ</unclear> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> ṣaṣirvarṣasahasrā<unclear>ṇi</unclear>
<lb n="21"/><unclear>vi</unclear>ṣṭāyāṁ jāyatē krimiḥ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 8*] bahubhirvasu<unclear>dā</unclear> dattā bahubhiccānupāli
<lb n="22" break="no"/>tā(n) <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> yesya yesya yedā bhūmi<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> tasya tasya dadā phalaṁ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 2*]
